data.description: !!Wow!!  2 Bedroom Townhome with 1.5 upgraded Bathrooms. Large living room with Fireplace, private patio. Includes NEW: Fridge, Stove, Dishwasher, Washer & Dryer. New Roof and exterior recently painted. Private courtyard where you can enjoy great evenings and relaxing after a long day. Detached 2 covered Parking slots. Gated Community with community pool, tennis courts, basketball courts and club house to host special events.   Situated near the World-Famous Las Vegas Strip, UNLV College, Shopping and Freeways. Se Habla Español.
